            <lg xml:id="TK297">
<l>poyyāmai poyyāmai yāṟṟi ṉaṟampiṟa</l>
<l>ceyyāmai ceyyāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a man has the power to abstain from falsehood, it will be well with him, even though he practise no other virtue.</l>
